tagram%20and%20X%20-%20to%20ensure%20users%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20violate%20the%20prohibited%20content%26quot%3B%20rule%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20as%20it%20bids%20to%20combat%20the%20worrying%20trend%20of%20deepfakes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fensure-users-dont-violate-content-rules-centre-to-it-firms-on-deepfakes-4746293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fensure-users-dont-violate-content-rules-centre-to-it-firms-on-deepfakes-4746293%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fensure-users-dont-violate-content-rules-centre-to-it-firms-on-deepfakes-4746293%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Introducing%20the%20hottest%20new%20place%20for%20singles%3A%20the%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20montage%20of%20people%20having%20crushes%20in%20airports.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657ca7730ec98e92f750196c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20hot%20new%20place%20to%20meet%20people.%20It's%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20individuals%20say%20they%20feel%20heightened%20sexual%20tension%20with%20other%20people%20their%20age%20while%20traveling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDating%20experts%20and%20therapists%20break%20down%20the%20phenomenon%20%E2%80%94%20known%20colloquially%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bairport%20crush.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20something%20strange%20going%20on%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20one%20specific%20airport%2C%20and%20really%2C%20it's%20not%20even%20about%20the%20airport%20itself.%20It's%20about%20the%20people%20there%2C%20all%20schlepping%20through%20the%20terminals%20with%20their%20rolling%20suitcases%20and%20U-shaped%20neck%20pillows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20they're%20all%20really%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20phenomenon%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ft%2FZT8mAgaAS%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20have%20taken%20to%20social%20media%20to%20unpack%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20the%20sudden%20realization%20that%20the%20person%20across%20from%20you%20in%20the%20boarding%20area%2C%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20about%20your%20age%2C%20is%20exceedingly%20and%20undeniably%20sexy.%20Young%20TikTokers%20have%20begun%20posting%20videos%20theorizing%20that%20the%20airport%2C%20a%20place%20that's%20simultaneously%20drab%20yet%20buzzing%20with%20energy%2C%20somehow%20makes%20other%20travelers%20seem%20irresistible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20it%20as%20having%20an%20%26quot%3Bairport%20crush%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20slipping%20on%20a%20pair%20of%20%26quot%3Bairport%20goggles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20when%20you've%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20drinks%20and%20those%20beer%20goggles%20come%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20media%20personality%20Josh%20Moss%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20you%20can't%20take%20them%20off%20until%20you're%20sober.%20It's%20the%20same%20thing%20when%20you're%20at%20the%20airport%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0you've%20got%20your%20'airport%20goggles'%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20hypnotized%2C%20you're%20in%20a%20state%2C%20and%20you%20can't%20get%20them%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20the%20allure%20of%20the%20airport%20hottie%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20an%20extent%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20the%20development%20of%20an%20airport%20crush%20comes%20down%20to%20a%20few%20things%3A%20proximity%2C%20similarity%2C%20and%20mystery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeigh%20Nor%C3%A9n%2C%20a%20Sweden-based%20sex%20therapist%20who%20specializes%20in%20sexual%20desire%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20geographical%20closeness%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfundamentals%20of%20attraction%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20why%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20people%20to%20develop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecut.com%2Farticle%2Foffice-ten-essay.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkplace%20or%20gym%20crushes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20a%20love%20affair%20with%20the%20guy%20from%20Gate%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20this%20is%20then%20applied%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Nor%C3%A9n%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20close%20to%20people%20geographically%20in%20an%20airport%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20you%20might%20be%20drawn%20to%20someone%20there%20in%20a%20different%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20find%20someone%20to%20be%20attracted%20to%20when%20you're%20stuck%20in%20a%20terminal%20with%20a%20relatively%20finite%20number%20of%20people.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20the%20added%20bonus%20of%20already%20having%20something%20in%20common%3A%20Whether%20you're%20traveling%20for%20vacation%2C%20work%2C%20or%20something%20different%20altogether%2C%20you're%20both%2C%20well%2C%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223701%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20standing%20in%20a%20boarding%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578d1e250edbc52a8638560%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrushes%20develop%20when%20you%20have%20both%20geographical%20closeness%20and%20something%20in%20common%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0making%20the%20airport%20a%20perfect%20place%20to%20find%20a%20crush.%3Cp%3ERobert%20Alexander%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20humans%2C%20our%20initial%20attraction%20to%20others%20is%20typically%20based%20on%20physical%20similarities%20with%20other%20people%2C%20said%20Beverly%20Palmer%2C%20professor%20emeritus%20of%20psychology%20at%20California%20State%20University%2C%20Dominguez%20Hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20that%20research%20shows%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%20or%20sexual%20attraction%20is%20that%20we%20tend%20to%20initially%20be%20drawn%20to%20people%20that%20are%20similar%20to%20our%20physical%20attractiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Palmer%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalmer%2C%20who%20wrote%20%26quot%3BLove%20Demystified%3A%20Strategies%20for%20a%20Successful%20Love%20Life%2C%26quot%3B%20held%20that%20attraction%20is%20largely%20based%20on%20physical%20similarities.%20Nor%C3%A9n%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20added%20that%20attraction%20can%20be%20based%20on%20similarities%20beyond%20looks%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20an%20affinity%20for%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20an%20airport%2C%20if%20you're%20flying%20to%20the%20same%20destination%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20some%20level%20of%20similarity%3A%20Either%20you%20live%20there%2C%20or%20you're%20both%20going%20there%20to%20work%2C%20or%20you're%20both%20going%20there%20for%20holiday%2C%26quot%3B%20Nor%C3%A9n%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20'great%20minds%20think%20alike'%20kind%20of%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20despite%20having%20built-in%20commonalities%2C%20there's%20an%20innate%20sense%20of%20mystery%20with%20an%20airport%20crush.%20You%20can%20let%20your%20imagination%20run%20wild%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20this%20person%20going%20to%20the%20same%20place%20as%20you%3F%20Are%20they%20unfathomably%20wealthy%2C%20and%20going%20to%20invite%20you%20to%20their%20cabin%20upstate%2C%20where%20you'll%20fall%20in%20love%20and%20one%20day%20raise%20a%20family%3F%20Who%20knows!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20left%20to%20the%20imagination%2C%20because%20you%20can%20be%20anybody%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20professional%20matchmaker%20Jacqueline%20Fae%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFae%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Florida-based%20matchmaking%20firm%20IDL%20Match%20Club%2C%20continued%2C%20saying%20that%20she%20can%20see%20how%20people%20start%20to%20envision%20a%20life%20with%20the%20sexy%20stranger%20from%20Terminal%20B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20all%20coming%20together%20at%20this%20airport%2C%20and%20it's%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20by%20yourself%20and%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20connect%20with%20somebody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAre%20they%20really%20a%2010%3F%20Or%20are%20your%20'airport%20goggles'%20on%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMoss%2C%20best%20known%20for%20his%20appearance%20on%20Love%20Island%20Australia%20in%202018%2C%20said%20he's%20had%20his%20share%20of%20airport%20crushes.%20The%20key%20to%20withstanding%20them%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20to%20determine%20whether%20or%20not%20your%20vision%20has%20been%20clouded%20by%20the%20fantasy%20of%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAirport%20goggles%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Moss%20called%20them%2C%20are%20akin%20to%20%26quot%3Bbeer%20goggles%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20term%20people%20use%20to%20describe%20finding%20others%20more%20attractive%20after%20having%20a%20few%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20leave%20the%20airport%2C%20you're%20out%20of%20that%20setting%2C%20and%20you've%20calmed%20down%2C%20then%20you%20can%20look%20and%20see%2C%20'OK%2C%20were%20my%20airport%20goggles%20fogging%20my%20judgment%3F%20Or%20are%20they%20really%20attractive%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cartoon%20man%20with%20heart%20eyes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578dd150ec98e92f74ec73c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHaving%20an%20airport%20crush%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20like%20having%20beer%20goggles%20on.%3Cp%3EGaeul%20Park%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20airport%20goggles%20could%20also%20be%20a%20biological%20response%20that%20can%20trick%20people%20into%20thinking%20it's%20love%20at%20first%20sight%20when%20it's%20really%20just%20nerves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20nervous%20flier%20and%20you%20find%20yourself%20experiencing%20an%20airport%20crush%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20might%20not%20actually%20be%20attraction%2C%26quot%3B%20Nor%C3%A9n%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20might%20just%20be%20nerves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudies%20have%20shown%20that%20humans%20can%20confuse%20anxiety%20for%20attraction%2C%20a%20concept%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Fblog%2Fmental-mishaps%2F201004%2Fis-love-or-too-much-caffeine-misattributions-arousal-strengthen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20misattribution%20of%20arousal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nor%C3%A9n%20pointed%20to%20the%20popular%20%26quot%3BBachelor%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20which%20often%20sends%20couples%20on%20adrenaline-pumping%20dates%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20sparking%20a%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20could%20be%20true%20for%20individuals%20with%20a%20fear%20of%20flying%2C%20said%20relationship%20expert%20and%20dating%20coach%20Samantha%20Jayne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnxiety%20and%20love%20are%20quite%20similar%2C%26quot%3B%20Jayne%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20you%20start%20to%20lock%20eyes%20with%20someone%2C%20and%20then%20you%20start%20to%20look%20for%20the%20pleasure%20in%20that%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20search%20for%20pleasure%20can%20easily%20disguise%20feelings%20of%20nervousness%20and%20anxiety%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0racing%20heart%2C%20sweaty%20palms%2C%20a%20tightening%20chest%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20feelings%20of%20affection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20apply%20this%20to%20an%20airport%20crush%2C%26quot%3B%20Nor%C3%A9n%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20bit%20nervous%2C%20or%20if%20you're%20just%20excited%20in%20general%2C%20you%20might%20more%20easily%20feel%20attracted%20to%20someone%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20because%20you're%20misinterpreting%20your%20bodily%20signals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2