0the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncreased%20stress%20pretty%20much%20always%20results%20in%20a%20shorter%20fuse%2C%20whether%20that's%20on%20a%20plane%20or%20on%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Price%2C%20an%20aviation%20professor%20at%20Colorado's%20Metropolitan%20State%20University%20of%20Denver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20have%20been%20hundreds%20of%20incidents%20this%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20US%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20FAA%20implemented%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Funruly-airline-passengers-the-faa-tries-memes-to-promote-peace-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bzero-tolerance%26quot%3B%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20unruly%20passengers%20after%20reports%20of%20misconduct%20by%20travelers%20jumped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20FAA%20has%20recorded%20more%20than%201%2C900%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Funruly-passenger-airplane-incident-bomb-threat-crew-punched-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bunruly%20passenger%26quot%3B%20reports.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that's%20significantly%20down%20from%20the%20record-high%20of%20nearly%206%2C000%20reports%20in%202021%2C%20agency%20data%20shows%20there%20are%20still%20more%20incidents%20compared%20to%20the%20years%20before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20available%20FAA%20data%2C%2039%20of%20the%20most%20serious%20of%20this%20year's%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20which%20included%20reports%20of%20physical%20assault%20against%20both%20passengers%20and%20crew%20members%20%E2%80%94%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Ffaa-refers-more-unruly-passenger-cases-fbi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereferred%20by%20the%20FAA%20to%20the%20FBI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20criminal%20investigation%20as%20of%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20cases%20of%20unruly%20plane%20passenger%20incidents%20have%20skyr