6quot%3BIn%20no%20case%2C%20however%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20anyone%20deserve%20to%20be%20physically%20assaulted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F01639625.2023.2234068%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20this%20year%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20academic%20journal%20Deviant%20Behavior%20found%20that%20unruly%20behavior%20by%20plane%20passengers%20was%20largely%20fueled%20by%20alcohol%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20at%20Dallas%20looked%20at%20data%20from%20more%20than%20915%20incidents%20reported%20to%20the%20Aviation%20Safety%20Reporting%20System%20over%2021%20years%20between%201999%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20number%20of%20instances%20that%20we%20reviewed%2C%20people%20were%20already%20intoxicated%20as%20they%20were%20boarding%20the%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.utdallas.edu%2Fsocial-sciences%2Fturbulent-air-passenger-behavior-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%2C%20Sheryl%20Skaggs%2C%20a%20sociology%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPassenger%20misconduct%20is%20the%20'new%20normal'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVance%20Hilderman%2C%20an%20aviation%20expert%20and%20CEO%20of%20aviation%20consulting%20firm%20AFuzion%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20bad%20behavior%20by%20airline%20passengers%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfortunately%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3Bnew%20normal.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20exacerbated%20by%20social%20media%20and%20copycats%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnruly%20passengers%20are%20called%20out%20more%20often%20and%20fellow%20passengers%20record%2C%20report%20%5Bit%5D%20far%20more%20often%2C%26quot%3B%20Hilderman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20delays%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbegets%20more%20frustrated%20passengers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funruly-plane-passengers-causes-airlines-experts-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703597401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b498a50edbc52a8645408%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funruly-plane-passengers-causes-airlines-experts-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stressful%20travel%20and%20changing%20social%20norms%20after%20the%20pandemic%20have%20shortened%20airline%20passengers'%20fuses%2C%20experts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmusumeci%40businessinsider.com%20(Natalie%20Musumeci)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funruly-plane-passengers-causes-airlines-experts-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Ill-Intention%26quot%3B%3A%20Siddaramaiah%20On%20Row%20Over%20Minister's%20Farmer%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFending%20off%20the%20BJP's%20attacks%20over%20one%20of%20his%20ministers%20allegedly%20claiming%20that%20farmers%20wish%20for%20droughts%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20loan%20waivers%2C%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20said%20that%20the%20remark%20was%20made%20in%20jest%20and%20that%20the%20minister%20could%20not%20have%20possibly%20had%20any%20ill-intention%20as%20he%20hails%20from%20a%20farming%20family%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20party%20is%20%26quot%3Banti-farmer%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20also%20appeared%20to%20caution%20members%20of%20his%20government%20against%20making%20%26quot%3Bcasual%20remarks%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20disrespectful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20row%2C%20Sugarcane%20Development%20Minister%20Shivananand%20Patil%2C%20has%20sparked%20controversies%20in%20the%20past%20as%20well%2C%20including%20when%20he%20had%20said%20in%20September%20that%20farmer%20suicides%20had%20gone%20up%20in%20Karnataka%20after%20the%20state%20government%20had%20hiked%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Mr%20Patil%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BKrishna%20(river)%20water%20is%20free%2C%20electricity%20is%20also%20free.%20Several%20Chief%20Ministers%20have%20given%20free%20seeds%20and%20manure.%20The%20farmers%20have%20only%20one%20wish%20-%20there%20should%20be%20a%20drought%20year%20after%20year%20so%20that%20their%20loans%20get%20waived.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20used%20the%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivanand-patil-siddaramaiah-karnataka-karnataka-ministers-farmers-drought-wish-remark-sparks-row-bjp-reacts-4738489%5C%22%3Eto%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20cabinet%20is%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20fools%26quot%3B.%20It%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-farmer%20government%26quot%3B%20is%20mocking%20and%20humiliating%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAgriculture%20Minister%20Shivanand%20Patil%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20a%20farming%20family%2C%20surely%20cannot%20have%20the%20intention%20to%20insult%20farmers.%20He%20has%20made%20some%20remarks%20in%20jest%20with%20the%20farmers%20around%20him.%20However%2C%20when%20applied%20to%20the%20entire%20farming%20community%2C%20these%20can%20be%20taken%20out%20of%20context%20and%20become%20offensive.%20This%20is%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt's%20crucial%20to%20speak%20with%20respect%20about%20farmers%20-%20our%20food%20providers.%20We%20must%20avoid%20making%20casual%20comments%20that%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20disrespectful.%20Adhering%20strictly%20to%20this%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20a%20responsibility%20for%20all.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAgriculture%20Minister%20Shivanand%20Patil%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20a%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Siddaramaiah%20(%40siddaramaiah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiddaramaiah%2Fstatus%2F1739617976280842487%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20remarks%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20Mr%20Patil%20and%20others%20in%20his%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20speak%20respectfully%20about%20farmers%2C%20who%20are%20food%20providers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20avoid%20making%20casual%20comments%20that%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20disrespectful.%20Adhering%20strictly%20to%20this%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20a%20responsibility%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrangling%20Farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remainder%20of%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah's%20post%20was%20devoted%20to%20attacking%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20%26quot%3Bstrangling%20farmers%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20well%20as%20highlighting%20his%20own%20government's%20pro-farmer%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%2C%20who%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers%20and%20are%20fundamentally%20anti-farmer%2C%20are%20waiting%20for%20opportunities%20like%20this%20to%20create%20controversy%20over%20Shivanand%20Patil's%20statements.%20When%20farmers%20asked%20for%20seeds%20and%20fertilisers%2C%20they%20were%20shot%20dead%3B%20when%20they%20asked%20for%20loan%20waivers%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20sarcastically%20remarked%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20note-printing%