%20functionaries%20should%20be%20in%20mission%20mode%20to%20achieve%20the%20target%20of%20crossing%2050%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20closed-door%20meeting%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20urged%20national%20office%20bearers%20to%20work%20in%20%26quot%3Bmission%20mode%26quot%3B%2C%20suggest%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20party%20recorded%20a%2037.4%25%20vote%20share%2C%20bagging%2022.9%20crore%20votes.%20On%20the%20seats%20it%20contested%20(435)%2C%20BJP%20recorded%2046.1%25%20vote%20share.%20On%20224%20of%20the%20303%20seats%20it%20won%20in%202019%2C%20the%20party%20snagged%20more%20than%2050%25%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2012%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20the%20party%20won%20more%20than%2050%25%20vote%20share%20-%20Jharkhand%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Himachal%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Goa%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%203-0%20win%20over%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20for%20the%20kill%2C%20aiming%20for%20a%20record%20of%20sorts%20in%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20party%20has%20ever%20achieved%2050%25%20vote%20share%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3B%20the%20Congress%20achieved%2048.1%25%20in%201984%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20BJP%20Achieve%2050%25%20Vote%20Share%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Increase%20vote%20share%20in%20seats%20it%20won%20in%202019%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20won%20303%20seats%20in%202019.%20There%20are%2095%20seats%20where%20it%20won%20all%20three%20polls%20-%202009%2C%202014%2C%20and%202019.%20It%20has%20won%20in%20two%20of%20three%20in%20167%20seats.%20So%2C%20there%20are%20262%20seats%20that%20can%20be%20classified%20as%20safe%20or%20relatively%20safe%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20can%20increase%20its%20vote%20share%20on%20these%20seats%20by%20better%20turnout%20management.%20Getting%20out%20more%20of%20its%20supporters%20to%20vote%20and%20thus%20winning%20these%20seats%20by%20even%20bigger%20margins.%20This%20strategy%20has%20been%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Gujarat%20effectively%20in%20past%20elections.%20However%2C%20this%20may%20not%20result%20in%20any%20additional%20seats%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Increase%20vote%20share%20in%20seats%20where%20it%20lost%20in%202019%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20runner%20up%20on%2072%20seats%20and%20finished%203rd%20on%2031%20seats.%20The%20party%20hopes%20to%20increase%20its%20vote%20share%20on%20these%20seats%20through%20better%20turnout%20management%2C%20local%20alliances%20and%20a%20pro-incumbency%20vote%20because%20of%20the%2010%20years%20of%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20This%20may%20or%20may%20not%20result%20in%20an%20additional%20number%20of%20seats%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Contest%20higher%20number%20of%20seats%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20need%20to%20contest%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20seats%20than%202019%20due%20to%20the%20exodus%20of%20allies.%20In%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20AIADMK%20have%20left%20the%20NDA.%20The%20party%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20contest%20more%20seats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20then%20add%20to%20the%20total%20votes%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20vote%20share.%20The%20party%20could%20even%20win%20a%20few%20more%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20while%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Punjab%20look%20difficult%20at%20this%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20these%20strategies%2C%20the%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20focus%20on%20Labharthis%20(beneficiaries)%2C%20women%20and%20first%20time%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20developed%20a%20loyal%20labharthi%20vote%20bank.%20According%20to%20a%20paper%20by%20Eshwaran%20Sreedharan%20for%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20nine%20key%20welfare%20programmes%20have%20benefited%2013%20to%2034%25%20of%20respondents%2Fvoters%2C%20with%20a%20large%20proportion%20crediting%20the%20central%20government%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20BJP%20or%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20hopes%20even%20more%20beneficiaries%20will%20back%20Modi%20in%202024%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20receiving%20the%20benefit%20of%20these%20schemes.%20To%20that%20end%2C%20extending%20free%20ration%20to%2080%20crore%20people%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20women%20have%20emerged%20as%20an%20important%20vote%20bloc%3B%20an%20increase%20in%20awareness%20and%20literacy%20levels%20has%20largely%20led%20women%20to%20make%20independent%20voting%20decisions.%20Increasingly%2C%20women%20have%20also%20been%20turning%20out%20in%20larger%20numbers%20than%20men%20and%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20voting%20cutting%20across%20caste%20and%20class%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20voting%20percentage%20of%20women%20was%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20men%20by%200.17%20per%20cent.%20In%202019%2C%2046%25%20women%20backed%20the%20NDA.%20In%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20state%20election%20recently%2C%2050%25%20women%20backed%20the%20BJP%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Axis%20My%20India%20survey%2C%20and%20the%20party%20hopes%20its%20women-focused%20schemes%2C%20along%20with%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%2C%20will%20bring%20it%20more%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20there%20were%201.5%20crore%20first%20time%20voters%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20around%202%25%20of%20the%20total%20voter%20base.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20total%20voting%20population%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20anywhere%20between%2095%20and%20100%20crore%2C%20meaning%202%20crore%20