aurant%2C%20says%20Nora%20Wunderwald%2C%20a%20publicity%20representative%20for%20St.%20Peter.%20After%20all%2C%20she%20says%2C%20patrons%2C%20who%20over%20the%20centuries%20have%20included%20Mozart%2C%20Faust%2C%20and%20Karl%20Lagerfeld%20(who%20was%20feted%20at%20the%20restaurant%20by%20Chanel)%2C%20needed%20some%20food%20to%20pair%20with%20their%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant's%20current%20operators%2C%20Veronika%20Kirchmair%20and%20Claus%20Haslauer%2C%20have%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20diversify%20the%20menu%20beyond%20schnitzel%20and%20strudel.%20This%20month's%20offerings%20include%20a%20confit%20fillet%20of%20char%2C%20artichoke%20Wellington%2C%20and%20an%20innovation%20Charlemagne%20and%20his%20compatriots%20would%20surely%20have%20marveled%20at%20brunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Olde%20Bell%2C%20est.%201135%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Lesson%3A%20Furniture%20can%20change%2C%20but%20service%20shouldn't%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20perhaps%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20King%20Stephen%20(he%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20reign%20warring%20with%20his%20cousin%20Matilda%2C%20the%20Holy%20Roman%20Empress)%2C%20you%20might%20pull%20into%20the%20Olde%20Bell%20Hotel%2C%20about%2035%20miles%20outside%20London%2C%20expecting%20to%20get%20a%20pint%20of%20ale%20and%20a%20hunk%20of%20bread%20to%20dip%20in%20your%20stew%20before%20you%20fell%20asleep%20on%20a%20mattress%20stuffed%20with%20horsehair%20and%2C%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20continued%20on%20your%20way%20across%20medieval%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20Olde%20Bell%20has%20expanded%20to%20include%20more%20guest%20quarters%20and%20a%20nuclear%20fallout%20shelter-turned-wine%20cellar%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20that%20every%20weary%20and%20thirsty%20traveler%20deserves%20a%20place%20to%20rest%20and%20a%20pint%20of%20ale%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20says%20sales%20manager%20Debi%20Hayes-%26quot%3Bexcept%20we've%20got%20comfier%20mattresses%20now!%26quot%3B%20History%2C%20of%20course%2C%20begets%20more%20history%2C%20with%20Winston%20Churchill%2C%20Boris%20Karloff%2C%20Franklin%20Delano%20Roosevelt%20and%20Elizabeth%20Taylor%20all%20having%20spent%20time%20in%20the%20hotel's%20cozy%20rooms%20and%20cozier%20bar%2C%20where%20sections%20of%20the%20original%20walls%20are%20covered%20with%20glass%20to%20keep%20them%20stable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanta%20Maria%20Novella%2C%20est.%201612%20(pharmacy%20from%201542)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Lesson%3A%20Signature%20products%20are%20signature%20products%20for%20a%20reason%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Gian%20Luca%20Perris%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20and%20%26quot%3Bnose%26quot%3B%20of%20Officina%20Profumo-Farmaceutica%20di%20Santa%20Maria%20Novella%2C%20the%20brand's%20most%20enduring%20fragrance%20is%20inextricably%20linked%20to%20its%20most%20famous%20patron%2C%20Catherine%20de'%20Medici.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcqua%20della%20Regina%2C%20with%20top%20notes%20of%20petitgrain%20and%20a%20base%20of%20musk%2C%20is%20still%20one%20of%20Santa%20Maria%20Novella's%20bestselling%20products%2C%20a%20chance%20for%20today's%20shoppers%20to%20capture%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20long-ago%20glamor%20and%20romance.%20In%20Perris'%20telling%2C%20in%201533%20the%20princess%2C%20as%20part%20of%20her%20wedding%20entourage%2C%20brought%20a%20perfume%20maker%20who%20was%20rumored%20to%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20Santa%20Maria%20Novella's%20friars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friars%2C%20who%20called%20the%20monastery%20of%20the%20Church%20of%20Santa%20Maria%20Novella%20home%2C%20had%20long%20dabbled%20in%20fragrant%20waters%2C%20often%20thought%20to%20keep%20the%20plague%20away.%20Catherine%2C%20possibly%20the%2016th%20century's%20most%20famous%20%26quot%3Bit%26quot%3B%20girl%2C%20was%20both%20a%20patron%20and%20something%20of%20a%20muse%20to%20the%20pharmacy%3B%20for%20her%20marriage%20scent%2C%20her%20perfumier%20was%20ready%20to%20create%20his%20greatest%20perfume%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20their%20upcoming%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Perris%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20created%20a%20bridal%20gift%20for%20Catherine's%20future%20husband%3A%20a%20perfume%20that%20enchanted%20the%20courts%20of%20France%20by%20embodying%20Florence's%20elegance%20and%20grace.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrooks%20Brothers%2C%20est.%201818%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Lesson%3A%20Focus%20on%20your%20core%20customer%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20as%20a%20small%20clothing%20manufacturer%20and%20shop%20in%20Lower%20Manhattan%2C%20Brooks%20Brothers%20has%20been%20supplying%20prep%20school%20students%20and%20Wall%20Street%20bankers%20with%20starched%20shirts%20and%20blue%20blazers%20for%20200%20years%2C%20pioneering%20the%20ready-to-wear%20suit%20and%20blanketing%20downtown%20office%20cores%20with%20retail%20locations%20stocked%20with%20in-case-of-emergency%20ties%20and%20pocket%20squares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ken%20Ohashi%20took%20over%20the%20company%20in%20late%202020%2C%20it%20was%20a%20strange%20moment%20for%20a%20brand%20that%20depended%20on%20people%20needing%20to%20dress%20up.%20For%20Ohashi%2C%20the%20key%20to%20outlasting%20Covid%20quarantines%20was%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20his%20die-hard%20customers%20might%20want%20more%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20casual%20wear.%20Items%20such%20as%20oversized%20striped%20rugby%20shirts%20and%20corduroy%20pants%20embroidered%20with%20jaunty%20hunting%20dogs%20now%20account%20for%2040%25%20of%20the%20company's%20business%2C%20up%20from%2020%25%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20Ohasi%20stresses%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Brooks%20Brothers%20sportswear%20is%20done%20the%20Brooks%20Brothers%20way.%20%26quot%3BOur%20core%20customer%20loves%20our%20sweatpants%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20you%20can%20get%20them%20monogrammed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsolidated%20Edison%2C%20est.%201823%20(as%20New%20York%20Gas%20Light%20Co.)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Lesson%3A%20Location%2C%20location%2C%20location%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConEd%2C%20an%20energy%20provider%20to%20New%20York%20City%20and%20many%20of%20its%20surrounding%20counties%20is%20the%20oldest%20continuously%20operating%20company%20listed%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%20It%20even%20predates%20Thomas%20Edison%20himself%20he%20was%20born%20in%201847%2C%20and%20the%20company%20that%20would%20someday%20bear%20his%20name%20was%20known%20as%20the%20New%20York%20Gas%20Light%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20dominated%20the%20market%20for%20gas%20lights%20across%20Manhattan%20(thanks%2C%20in%20part%2C%20to%20a%20little%20help%20from%20the%20bosses%20of%20Tammany%20Hall)%2C%20the%20company-renamed%20New%20York%20Steam%20Co.%20in%20the%20early%201880s%20was%20primed%20to%20become%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20newly%20electrified%20NYC%20of%20the%20late%2019th%20century.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20the%20only%20business%20with%20designs%20on%20(literal)%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%201890s%20no%20fewer%20than%2030%20companies%20sought%20to%20provide%20electricity%20to%20the%20homes%20and%20businesses%20of%20New%20York%20and%20Westchester%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dan%20Taft%2C%20a%20chief%20engineer%20in%20central%20operations%20at%20ConEd%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20laying%20the%20original%20electric%20feeder%20cables%20in%20the%20streets%20of%20Lower%20Manhattan%20in%201882%2C%20Edison%20was%20so%20impressed%20with%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pipe-laying%20work%20being%20done%20simultaneously%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Steam%20Co.%20that%20he%20made%20arrangements%20to%20send%20surplus%20steam%20from%20his%20Pearl%20Street%20Station%20into%20the%20steam%20system%2C%20thereby%20becoming%20the%20very%20first%20co-generator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20mid-1920s%20the%20competition%20had%20been%20mostly%20wiped%20out%2C%20leaving%20ConEd%20(the%20name%20became%20official%20in%201936)%20the%20sole%20source%20of%20electric%20light%20in%20a%20city%20that%20uses%20a%20lot%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703592360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fh25qk848_business_120x90_26_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecrets-of-worlds-oldest-businesses-some-dating-back-to-578-ad-803-ad-4745210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20American%20business%20closes%20shop%20after%20about%2021%20years.%20(Spare%20a%20thought%20for%20those%20enterprises%20in%20the%20back%20half%20of%20the%20bell%20curve%2C%20which%20never%20reach%20the%20legal%20drinking%20age.)%20Some%20businesses%2C%20though%2C%20last%20longer%20lot%20longer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecrets-of-worlds-oldest-businesses-some-dating-back-to-578-ad-803-ad-4745210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecrets-of-worlds-oldest-businesses-some-dating-back-to-578-ad-803-ad-4745210%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecrets-of-worlds-oldest-businesses-some-dating-back-to-578-ad-803-ad-4745210%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Panera%20founder%20says%20one%20of%20his%20biggest%20regrets%20is%20not%20firing%20people%20faster%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he's%20even%20received%20thank-you's%20afterward%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ron%20Shaich%20serving%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5462240669bedd064877990e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERon%20Shaich%3Cp%3EPanera%2FDavid%20Elmes%3C