king%20surgery%20that%20removes%20the%20brain%20tissue%20that%20causes%20seizures.%C2%A0Ten%20weeks%20after%20the%20surgery%2C%20the%20teenager%20has%20not%20had%20a%20single%C2%A0episode%2C%20according%20to%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20had%20such%20a%20long%20period%20not%20having%20a%20seizure%2C%20it's%20an%20amazing%20relief.%20I'm%20so%20happy.%20Christmas%20is%20a%20big%20occasion%20and%20now%20it%20will%20be%20even%20bigger%20this%20year.%20Being%20able%20to%20have%20this%20surgery%20is%20amazing.%20I%20think%20it%20could%20change%20my%20life%20forever%20by%20making%20me%20able%20to%20do%20the%20things%20I%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20do%2C''%20Mr%20Bain%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-edinburgh-east-fife-67762097%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20Scotland%20News%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surgery%20was%20conducted%20at%20the%20Edinburgh%20Children's%20Hospital%20in%20October.%20The%20innovative%20laser%20technology%20known%20as%20MRI-guided%20Laser%20Interstitial%20Thermal%20Therapy%20(LITT)%C2%A0%20is%20minimally%20invasive%20and%20the%20surgery%20takes%20just%20under%20two%20hours%20with%20a%20relatively%20short%20recovery%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20procedure%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20his%20brain%20that%20caused%20the%20attacks%20was%20removed%20by%20laser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20laser%20surgery%20is%20a%20fantastic%20development%20for%20specific%20patients%20and%20will%20give%20some%20with%20epilepsy%20a%20real%20chance%20to%20live%20a%20normal%20life.%20The%20surgery%20has%20been%20life-changing%20not%20just%20for%20Angus%2C%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20family%2C''%C2%A0Dr.%20Jothy%20Kandasamy%2C%20consultant%20neurosurgeon%20at%20the%20Royal%20Hospital%20for%20Children%20and%20Young%20People%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20who%20lives%20in%20Gateside%2C%20Fife%2C%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20epilepsy%20when%20he%20was%20four%20years%20old.%20Since%20then%20he%20has%20been%20on%20lots%20of%20heavy%20medication%2C%20tests%2C%20and%20scans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20Nicki%20Bain%2C%2048%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20lives%20have%20been%20consumed%20with%20Angus's%20epilepsy%20since%20he%20was%20four.%20He%20has%20been%20on%20lots%20of%20very%20heavy%20medication%2C%20had%20wires%20in%20his%20head%2C%20brain%20stimulation%2C%20and%20so%20many%20tests%20and%20scans.%20The%20build-up%20to%20him%20having%20a%20seizure%20would%20last%20a%20few%20days%2C%20then%20after%20the%20seizure%20it%20would%20take%20another%20couple%20of%20days%20for%20him%20to%20recover%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20think%20he's%20ever%20actually%20had%20a%20normal%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20said%20he%20hopes%20to%20one%20day%20get%20his%20driver's%20license%2C%20play%20rugby%2C%20or%20go%20skiing%2C%20things%20that%20had%20been%20too%20risky%20for%20him%20to%20do%20pre-surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703591280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F491ppdpg_surgery-generic_625x300_26_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscottish-teen-seizure-free-after-groundbreaking-surgery-that-removed-part-of-his-brain-4745659%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20procedure%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20his%20brain%20that%20caused%20the%20epileptic%20attacks%20was%20removed%20by%20laser.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscottish-teen-seizure-free-after-groundbreaking-surgery-that-removed-part-of-his-brain-4745659%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscottish-teen-seizure-free-after-groundbreaking-surgery-that-removed-part-of-his-brain-4745659%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscottish-teen-seizure-free-after-groundbreaking-surgery-that-removed-part-of-his-brai