ol%20ditching%20to%20produce%20minimal%20debris.%20It%20was%20performed%20to%20not%20be%20trapped%20or%20found.%20Certainly%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20not%20visible%20except%20for%20the%20military.%20The%20guy%20knew%20that%20if%20search%20and%20rescue%20would%20be%20triggered%2C%20it%20would%20be%20on%20the%20flight%20path%2C''%20Mr%20Marchad%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20further%20argued%20that%20the%20plane's%20transponder%20was%20turned%20off%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BU-turn%26quot%3B%20it%20did%20away%20from%20the%20flight%20path%20could%20not%20have%20been%20autopilot.%20They%20further%20noted%20that%20the%20sudden%20change%20in%20direction%20occurred%20when%20the%20plane%20was%20in%20a%20''no%20man's%20land''%2C%20between%20Thai%2C%20Indonesian%2C%20Indian%2C%20and%20Malay%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20flight%20MH370%20with%20227%20passengers%20and%2012%20crew%20members%20on%20board%20disappeared%20after%20leaving%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20Airport%20in%20southern%20Malaysia%20en%20route%20to%20Beijing%2C%20China%2C%20on%20March%208%2C%202014.%20Even%20after%20massive%20search%20operations%2C%20its%20wreckage%20was%20not%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20back%2C%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-fisherman-claims-he-found-part-of-mh370-i-wish-id-never-seen-the-thing-4709281%5C%22%3E%20fisherman%20in%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20that%20he%20found%20a%20large%20piece%20of%20the%20missing%20plane%20but%20was%20ignored%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703587320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fuslli2a_mh-370_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmissing-flight-mh370-could-be-found-in-days-with-new-search-claim-experts-4745273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aerospace%20experts%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20mystery%20of%20the%20flight's%20whereabouts%20cou