US%20marks%20the%2080th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Exclusion%20Act%2C%20thousands%20of%20Chinese%20immigrants%20are%20crossing%20the%20US-Mexico%20border%20after%20witnessing%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20Chinese%20economy.%20From%20January%20through%20September%2C%20over%2024%2C000%20Chinese%20migrants%20crossed%20the%20border%20without%20authorization%2C%20about%2013%20times%20the%20number%20recorded%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20Chinese%20migrants%20who%20cross%20into%20the%20US%20without%20authorization%20usually%20wait%20for%20agents%20from%20the%20US%20Border%20Patrol%20to%20pick%20them%20up.%20Chinese%20migrants%20were%20granted%20asylum%20nearly%2067%25%20of%20the%20time%20in%20immigration%20courts%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthousands-of-chinese-migrants-cross-border-as-us-marks-80th-anniversary-of-repeal-of-exclusion-act%2Farticleshow%2F106288763.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthousands-of-chinese-migrants-cross-border-as-us-marks-80th-anniversary-of-repeal-of-exclusion-act%2Famp_articleshow%2F106288763.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthousands-of-chinese-migrants-cross-border-as-us-marks-80th-anniversary-of-repeal-of-exclusion-act%2Famp_articleshow%2F106288763.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22If%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20Ain't%20Broke%2C%20Break%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F12180417%2FIMG_3931.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20ain%E2%80%99t%20broke%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20fix%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dictionary%20says%20this%20is%20a%20proverbial%20saying%20whose%20popularity%20is%20attributed%20to%20an%20official%20in%20former%20US%20President%20Jimmy%20Carter%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20say%20that%20one%20should%20not%20try%20to%20change%20something%20that%20is%20working%20well%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20is%20150%20years%20old.%20It%20has%20worked%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20also%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20calls%20itself%20an%20Islamic%20republic%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20post-1947%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20laws%20have%20remained%20the%20same%20that%20the%20British%20had%20left%20behind%20and%20are%20common%20across%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%20Penal%20Code%20written%20by%20Thomas%20Macaulay%20in%20the%201830s%20and%20enforced%20from%201862%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Penal%20Code%20remain%20almost%20identical.%20The%20changes%20that%20came%20in%20after%201947%20are%20few%20on%20either%20side.%20The%20natives%20of%20Lahore%20know%20what%20the%20number%20144%20(Section%20144%2C%20which%20criminalises%20assembling%20of%20people%20under%20certain%20circumstances)%20means%20in%20law%20just%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laws%20were%20familiar%20and%20they%20were%20functional.%20Everyone%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Ethanedar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20constable%20to%20the%20citizen%20knew%20them.%20For%20Pakistanis%2C%20just%20as%20for%20Indians%2C%20the%20law%20that%20deals%20with%20punishing%20murder%20is%20called%20302%20and%20the%20one%20for%20cheating%20is%20420.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20numbers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20that%20have%20been%20used%20on%20the%20subcontinent%20even%20after%20Independence%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%20Because%20the%20laws%20work.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20the%20courts%20clogged%20with%20cases%2C%20it%20is%20not%20because%20the%20laws%20are%20flawed%20and%20the%20new%20laws%20will%20not%20change%20that%20(in%20fact%20the%20contrary%2C%20as%20we%20will%20see).%20If%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20colonial%20laws%20are%20unsuitable%20for%20a%20free%20nation%20and%20we%20need%20a%20more%20liberal%20order%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-withdraws-3-criminal-law-bills-to-make-changes-recommended-by-parl-panel%5C%22%3Ethen%20also%20the%20Sanhita%20does%20not%20change%20that%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20demand%20in%20India%20that%20the%20laws%20be%20changed.%20We%20are%20not%20referring%20to%20tinkering%2C%20meaning%20removing%20and%20adding%20that%20which%20becomes%20necessary%20with%20changing%20times.%20We%20are%20referring%20to%20changes%20brought%20about%20from%20the%20whole%20cloth.%20Taking%20down%20an%20edifice%20fully%20and%20dismantling%20it%20without%20reason.%20The%20question%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%3A%20Why%20change%20something%20that%20is%20working%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20that%20we%20do%20not%20have%20and%20will%20not%20get.%20The%20script%20writers%20of%20Bollywood%20will%20need%20to%20change%20their%20dialogues%20and%20get%20their%20screen%20judges%20and%20cops%20to%20memorise%20some%20new%20numbers%2C%20but%20deeper%20problems%20are%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20that%20the%20new%20laws%20would%20likely%20increase%20litigation.%20Lawyer%20Sanjay%20Hegde%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20after%20making%20bounced%20cheques%20a%20criminal%20offence%2C%20courts%20have%20been%20flooded%20with%20new%20litigation%20on%20this.%20Lawyer%20Colin%20Gonsalves%20has%20asked%20why%20the%20police%20were%20being%20given%20more%20arbitrary%20powers%20over%20citizens%20than%20even%20in%20the%20colonial%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyer%20and%20Congressman%20Abhishek%20%E2%80%9CManu%E2%80%9D%20Singhvi%20has%20asked%20why%20the%20non-existent%20(according%20to%20the%20government%20itself)%20phenomenon%20of%20%E2%80%9Clove%20jihad%E2%80%9D%20was%20being%20added%20to%20offences%20with%20a%2010-year%20sentence.%20Yet%20others%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20sedition%2C%20under%20a%20new%20name%2C%20remains%20under%20the%20penal%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simplest%20way%20of%20understanding%20this%20masterstroke%20is%20to%20accept%20that%20they%20are%20masterstrokes%20and%20not%20question%20their%20necessity%20or%20wisdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcriminal-bills-drafting-shoddy-sakshya-nyay-sanhita-ipc-evidence%5C%22%3EShoddy%20Drafting%20Has%20Left%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20New%20Criminal%20Bills%20With%20Glaring%20Errors%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Army%20Chief%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%20has%20written%20his%20memoirs%20and%20if%20they%20are%20allowed%20to%20be%20published%2C%20they%20contain%20the%20revelation%20that%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbolt%20from%20the%20blue%E2%80%9D.%20Something%20modest%20by%20way%20of%20a%20short%20service%20commission%20that%20the%20Army%20had%20proposed%20was%20first%20inverted.%20Instead%20of%20retaining%20three-fourths%20of%20the%20inductees%2C%20only%20one-fourth%20would%20be%20and%20the%20rest%20out%20to%20pasture%2C%20retired%20at%20ages%20as%20young%20as%2022.%20And%20the%20plan%20was%20extended%20to%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20which%20had%20no%20inclination%20toward%20or%20need%20for%20this%20%E2%80%9Creform%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeaning%20it%20was%20a%20top-down%20and%20unexpected%20stroke%20of%20genius%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(since%20nobody%20else%20counts).%20This%20has%20changed%20the%20face%20of%20an%20Army%20that%20has%20been%20functioning%20competently%20since%20the%2018th%20century%2C%20meaning%20for%20over%20200%20years.%20Why%20agitate%20and%20disturb%20something%20that%20works%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20question%20could%20also%20be%20asked%20of%20the%20brilliant%20decision%20to%20abolish%20the%20vast%20bulk%20of%20our%20currency%20in%20November%202016.%20Who%20was%20asking%20for%20Rs%201%2C000%20and%20Rs%20500%20notes%20to%20be%20banned%3F%20Not%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20which%20resisted%20and%20warned%2C%20correctly%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20that%20this%20was%20a%20dumb%20move%20that%20would%20damage%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20the%20economists%20and%20not%20the%20business%20community%20and%20certainly%20not%20citizens.%20It%20came%20because%20of%20a%20whim.%20The%20same%20mentality%20is%20at%20work%20with%20the%20new%20criminal%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20not%20only%20require%20the%20judiciary%2C%20police%2C%20lawyers%20and%20the%20public%20to%20know%20new%20laws%20but%20it%20will%20also%20endanger%20settled%20jurisprudence%20on%20the%20old%20laws%20and%20open%20up%20all%20sorts%20of%20minor%20and%20major%20problems%20that%20currently%20do%20not%20exist.%20Precedents%2C%20the%20basis%20of%20common%20law%2C%20which%20we%20follow%2C%20will%20come%20undone.%20Whose%20then%20was%20asking%20for%20a%20change%3F%20Not%20the%20judges%20or%20the%20police%20or%20lawyers%20or%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyer%20Sanjay%20Hegde%20has%20warned%20that%20once%20introduced%2C%20our%20new%20Sanhita%20will%20be%20even%20more%20disruptive%20than%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20hopes%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20case%20and%20hope%20also%2C%20despite%20the%20evidence%20of%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20that%20adequate%20thought%20and%20preparation%20have%20gone%20into%20this%20introduction%20of%20change%20where%20none%20was%20really%20required.%20And%20for%20those%20who%20remain%20puzzled%20and%20still%20ask%20the%20question%3A%20Why%20are%20we%20doing%20this%3F%20The%20answer%20appears%20to%20lie%20in%20a%20mindset%20that%20believes%20%E2%80%9Cit%20ain%E2%80%99t%20broke%2C%20then%20break%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703579471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F12180417%2FIMG_3931.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-the-indian-penal-code-aint-broke-break-it%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20was%20no%20demand%20in%20India%20that%20the%20laws%20be%20changed.%20We%20are%20not%20referring%20to%20tinkering%2C%20meaning%20removing%20and%20adding%20that%20which%20becomes%20necessary%20with%20changing%20times.%20We%20are%20referring%20to%20taking%20down%20an%20edifice%20fully%20and%20dismantling%20it%20without%20reason.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-the-indian-penal-code-aint-broke-break-it%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poonch%20Civilians'%20Army%20Custody%20Death%3A%20FIR%20Invokes%20Section%20302%20of%20IPC%2C%20Injured%20Victim%20Notes%20Torture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24194348%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-24-at-6.20.20-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20first%20information%20report%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%2C%20allegedly%20in%20Army%20custody%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Poonch%2C%20has%20invoked%20the%20murder%20clause%2C%20Section%20302%2C%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fpoonch-rajouri-custodial-deaths-police-file-fir-against-unknown-personnel%2Farticle67674689.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20on%20the%20FIR%2C%20filed%20in%20the%20Surankote%20police%20station%20against%20%E2%80%98unknown%E2%80%99%20accused%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20death%20of%20the%20three%20came%20as%20two%20videos%20were%20circulated%2C%20showing%20civilians%20being%20brutally%20beaten%20and%20tortured%20by%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20men%20in%20Army%20uniform.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoonch-civilians-killed-are-among-the-men-seen-in-video-being-tortured-by-soldiers-sarpanch-confirms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20confirmed%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20three%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20belong%20to%20Topa%20Peer%20village%20and%20are%20members%20of%20the%20Gujjar%20Bakarwal%20community%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe.%20Five%20others%2C%20also%20picked%20up%20for%20questioning%2C%20are%20undergoing%20treatment%20and%20are%20grievously%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20them%2C%2052-year-old%20Mohammad%20Ashraf%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcivilian-killed-tortured-poonch-video-chilli-powder-wounds-9082781%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20one%20of%20those%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20and%20noted%20that%20chilli%20powder%20was%20rubbed%20on%20wounds%20created%20by%20the%20beatings%20that%20they%20were%20subjected%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshraf%20speaking%20from%20his%20hospital%20bed%2C%20claimed%20he%20and%20four%20others%20were%20picked%20up%20by%20security%20forces%20last%20week%20after%20which%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20removed%20our%20clothes%20and%20beat%20us%20with%20lathis%20and%20iron%20rods%2C%20and%20rubbed%20chilli%20powder%20on%20our%20wounds%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamily%20members%20and%20neighbours%20of%20the%20three%20deceased%20%E2%80%93%20Safeer%20Hussain%20(48)%2C%20Mohammad%20Showkat%20(28)%20and%20Shabbir%20Ahmad%20(25)%20%E2%80%93%20said%20their%20bodies%2C%20once%20handed%20over%20to%20their%20families%2C%20appeared%20severely%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20has%20ordered%20a%20court%20of%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20such%20a%20cognizable%20offence%20under%20section%20302%20of%20IPC%20is%20made%20out.%20On%20this%20information%20instant%20case%20stands%20registered.%20As%20the%20instant%20case%20is%20of%20special%20nature%20which%20is%203rd%20of%20its%20kind%20from%20the%20said%20village%20and%203rd%20of%20its%20kind%20during%20the%20current%20year%2C%20whereas%2041st%20case%20of%20special%20nature%20of%20current%20year%2C%20Special%20report-A%20will%20be%20submitted%20separately%20and%20investigation%20taken%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20FIR%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0report%20also%20quotes%20local%20MP%20Gulam%20Ali%2C%20who%20was%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%202022%2C%20as%20having%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20a%20professional%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703579447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24194348%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-24-at-6.20.20-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoonch-civilians-army-custody-death-fir-invokes-section-302-of-ipc-injured-victim-notes-torture%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2252-year-old%20Mohammad%20Ashraf%20has%20told%20Indian%20Express%20that%20he%20was%20one%20of%20those%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20and%20noted%20that%20chilli%20powder%20was%20rubbed%20on%20wounds%20created%20by%20the%20beatings%20that%20they%20were%20subjected%20to.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoonch-civilians-army-custody-death-fir-invokes-section-302-of-ipc-injured-victim-notes-torture%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Orry%20reveals%20gossip%20from%20SRK's%20birthday%20bash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703577042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106287145%2Cimgsize-46174.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimeso