tice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25170033%2Fimage-1669.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22908%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25170033%2Fimage-1669.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25170033%2Fimage-1669-300x167.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690701%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBaloch%20women%20leading%20the%20march.%20Photo%3A%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjmal%20further%20shared%20that%20his%20family%20is%20too%20impoverished%20to%20afford%20meals%2C%20and%20some%20days%20they%20go%20without%20eating.%20The%20family%20has%20received%20threats%20from%20the%20security%20forces%20not%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20protest.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CTD%20has%20a%20mandate%20to%20abduct%20and%20kill%20Balochs%2C%20and%20we%20can%20no%20longer%20tolerate%20such%20brutal%20actions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20state%E2%80%99s%20fear%20over%20Balochs%20participating%20in%20the%20march%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefusing%20to%20bury%20Balach%E2%80%99s%20dead%20body%20and%20demanding%20justice%2C%20the%20family%20initiated%20a%20sit-in%20at%20Shaheed%20Fida%20Chowk.%20This%20protest%20evolved%20into%20the%20march%20against%20the%20Baloch%20Genocide%20on%20December%206%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%20led%20the%20march.%20Mahrang%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20it%20is%20not%20just%20a%20march%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20the%20main%20leader%20spearheading%20the%20march%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20Baloch%20women%20have%20joined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahrang%20shared%20that%20in%20her%20province%2C%20not%20a%20single%20house%20remains%20whose%20family%20member%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20faced%20enforced%20disappearance%20or%20been%20killed.%20What%20sets%20this%20march%20apart%20is%20that%20the%20Balach%20family%20refused%20to%20bury%20their%20son%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20sent%20a%20strong%20message.%20The%20widespread%20participation%20of%20common%20people%20also%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20powerful%20march%2C%20reflecting%20the%20collective%20frustration%20with%20death%20squads%2C%20CTD%2C%20and%20enforced%20disappearances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20state%2C%20being%20a%20Baloch%20is%20considered%20a%20sin%2C%20and%20we%20are%20being%20killed%20simply%20for%20being%20Baloch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahrang%20said%2C%20with%20a%20sorrowful%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20facing%20threats%20from%20the%20government%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20march%20lacked%20financial%20support.%20The%20sole%20contribution%20from%20common%20people%20allowed%20the%20march%20to%20continue.%20Despite%20all%20the%20hurdles%2C%20when%20the%20government%20realised%20they%20could%20not%20quell%20the%20protest%2C%20they%20resorted%20to%20violence%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20march%20has%20made%20the%20following%20demands%20to%20Islamabad%3A%20the%20UN%20should%20send%20a%20fact-finding%20mission%20to%20investigate%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20Balochistan%3B%20the%20Balochistan%20CTD%20must%20admit%20its%20role%20in%20the%20fake%20encounter%20that%20led%20to%20Balach%E2%80%99s%20death%3B%20release%20all%20forcibly%20disappeared%20Balochs%2C%20especially%20those%20whose%20kin%20are%20present%20at%20the%20sit-in%3B%20and%20remove%20state-supported%20death%20squads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20should%20issue%20an%20acknowledgment%20for%20enforced%20disappearances%2C%20conduct%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20names%2C%20and%20stop%20filing%20fake%20FIRs%20against%20peaceful%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20police%20tortured%20and%20beat%20protesters%20when%20they%20entered%20Islamabad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20march%20entered%20Islamabad%2C%20the%20police%20prevented%20them%20from%20proceeding%20to%20the%20Islamabad%20Press%20Club%2C%20where%20other%20Baloch%20victim%20families%20were%20already%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20was%20peaceful%2C%20yet%20the%20police%20created%20hurdles%20and%20blocked%20their%20path%20to%20the%20Press%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20the%20protesters%20held%20a%20protest%20on%20the%20road%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahrang%20announced%20that%20the%20Baloch%20victim%20families%20present%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20should%20join%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20148px)%2085vw%2C%20148px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25172929%2Fimage-1670-148x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22148%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25172929%2Fimage-1670-148x300.png%20148w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25172929%2Fimage-1670.png%20330w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20kids%20holding%20a%20placard%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20also%20Mahrang.%20How%20many%20Mahrang%20can%20you%20arrest%3F%20Long%20live%20resistance.%E2%80%99%20Photo%3A%20Wahab%20Baloch%2C%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20peaceful%20intentions%2C%20the%20police%20brutally%20arrested%20all%20protesters%2C%20sparking%20viral%20videos%20and%20global%20attention.%20The%20government%2C%20after%20using%20violence%2C%20tried%20to%20send%20them%20back%20to%20Quetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaloch%20women%20questioned%20why%20they%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20continue%20their%20peaceful%20protest.%20They%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CAren%E2%80%99t%20we%20citizens%20of%20the%20state%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesters%20said%20that%20they%20would%20not%20return%20to%20Quetta%20until%20their%20demands%20were%20addressed%2C%20insisting%20on%20the%20release%20of%20all%20protesters%20and%20an%20end%20to%20the%20FIRs%20against%20them%20in%20both%20Islamabad%20and%20Balochistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahrang%2C%20who%20is%20now%20a%20symbol%20of%20resistance%20among%20the%20victims%2C%20said%20that%20Balochistan%20will%20not%20tolerate%20ruthless%20policies.%20She%20said%20that%20whenever%20the%20state%20attempts%20to%20oppress%20Balochs%2C%20they%20will%20return%20and%20peacefully%20resist.%20They%20will%20continue%20to%20expose%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20just%20as%20we%20did%20in%20Islamabad%20through%20the%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Baloch%2C%20a%20victim%20of%20forced%20disappearances%2C%20questioned%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20their%20peaceful%20protest%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20they%20treat%20the%20missing%20persons%2C%20who%20are%20in%20their%20custody%2C%20with%20such%20brutality%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20state%20commits%20genocide%20against%20Balochs%20and%20kills%20them%20in%20extrajudicial%20killing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chairman%20of%20Voice%20for%20Baloch%20Missing%20Persons%2C%20Nasrullah%20Baloch%2C%20said%20that%20since%20the%20Musharraf%20era%2C%20Baloch%20people%20have%20been%20disappearing%2C%20and%20their%20mutilated%20bodies%20have%20been%20dumped%20on%20the%20roads.%20Since%202009%2C%20missing%20persons%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20extrajudicial%20killings%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20death%20toll%20of%20more%20than%202%2C000%20Balochs.%20Since%202021%2C%20over%20200%20Balochs%20have%20been%20murdered%20in%20fake%20encounters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20the%20government%20aimed%20to%20instill%20fear%20in%20the%20Balochs%20through%20extrajudicial%20killings.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20that%20this%20march%20sends%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20establishment%3A%20Balochs%20will%20no%20longer%20accept%20the%20kill-and-dump%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20civilians%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20no%20authority%20to%20even%20comment%20on%20Balochistan%E2%80%99s%20situation.%20Criticising%20the%20judiciary%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Pakistan%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa%2C%20while%20in%20Balochistan%2C%20has%20neglected%20the%20issue%20of%20missing%20persons.%20The%20judiciary%20scarcely%20addresses%20the%20concerns%20of%20Baloch%20women%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBalochistan%20is%20run%20by%20the%20military%20establishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahrang%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20decide%20who%20should%20be%20in%20the%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20noted%20that%20whether%20politicians%20or%20judges%2C%20those%20seeking%20power%20adopt%20an%20anti-State%20stance%2C%20but%20once%20in%20power%2C%20they%20become%20the%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20establishment.%20The%20solution%20to%20Balochistan%E2%80%99s%20issues%20lies%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20those%20who%20authorise%20the%20killing%20of%20Balochs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703568609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25173916%2Fimage-1671.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-baloch-women-protest-extrajudicial-killings-forced-disappearances%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%202009%2C%20missing%20persons%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20extrajudicial%20killings%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20death%20toll%20of%20more%20than%202%2C000%20Balochs.%20According%20to%20activists%2C%20since%202021%2C%20over%20200%20Balochs%20ha