DVAC%20search%20team%20was%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20chamber%20of%20accused%20officer%20Ankit%20Tiwari%20for%20more%20than%20three%20hours.%20The%20Assistant%20Director%20informed%20that%20the%20Deputy%20Director%20was%20in%20Chennai%20and%20was%20air%20dashing%20to%20Madurai%20to%20approve%20the%20search.%20But%20he%20did%20not%20come%E2%80%A6%20we%20had%20to%20seek%20the%20assistance%20of%20the%20local%20police%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20search%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20DVAC%20official%20told%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20too%20claims%20to%20be%20probing%20both%20Tiwari%20as%20well%20as%20officers%20of%20the%20DVAC.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fed-vs-tn-cops-agency-shifts-case-to-delhi-hq%2Farticleshow%2F106276481.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20moved%20this%20probe%20out%20of%20the%20state%20to%20its%20New%20Delhi%20headquarters.%20ED%20sources%20reportedly%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20this%20was%20because%20of%20fears%20of%20meddling%20from%20the%20local%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claims%20had%20previously%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20DVAC%20officers%20with%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%2C%20which%20did%20not%20register%20an%20FIR.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fbribery-case-tn-cops-ask-ed-officer-to-appear-at-police-station-on-dec-26-2824801%5C%22%3Emedia%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Beniwal%E2%80%99s%20complaints%20from%20December%202%20had%20accused%20the%20DVAC%20team%20of%20accessing%20sensitive%20case%20records%2C%20information%20and%20internal%20documents%20of%20the%20ED%20related%20to%20other%20cases%20which%20have%20no%20link%20with%20the%20alleged%20search%20case%2C%20and%20ransacking%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20entire%20office%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20office