0Hemant%20Munjal%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-vivo-india-executives-arrested-in-money-laundering-case-4729959%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20December%2023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20months%20earlier%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20arrested%20the%20Lava%20International%20managing%20director%20Hari%20Om%20Rai%2C%20Chinese%20national%20Guangwen%20alias%20Andrew%20Kuang%2C%20and%20chartered%20accountants%20Nitin%20Garg%20and%20Rajan%20Malik%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20same%20case.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20in%20judicial%20custody%20at%20present.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20officials%20of%20the%20Chinese%20firm%20in%20India%2C%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said%20that%20Beijing%20was%20%E2%80%9Cclosely%20following%E2%80%9D%20the%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBacking%20the%20Chinese%20firm%2C%20she%20advised%20India%20to%20create%20an%20equitable%20business%20environment%20for%20all%20foreign%20companies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chinese%20government%20firmly%20supports%20Chinese%20businesses%20in%20safeguarding%20their%20lawful%20rights%20and%20interests.%20We%20hope%20that%20India%20will%20fully%20recognise%20the%20mutually%20beneficial%20nature%20of%20the%20business%20cooperation%20between%20our%20two%20countries%20and%20provide%20a%20fair%2C%20just%2C%20transparent%20and%20non-discriminatory%20business%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20stated%20that%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20and%20consulates%20in%20India%20would%20continue%20offering%20consular%20protection%20and%20assistance%20to%20the%20individuals%20concerned%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%2C%20in%20its%20court%20documents%20for%20the%20first%20four%20detainees%2C%20has%20asserted%20that%20they%20helped%20Vivo%20India%20gain%20unjust%20profits%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20posed%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20sovereignty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20July%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20raided%20Vivo%20India%20based%20on%20allegations%20that%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%E2%80%9D%20transferred%20Rs%2062%2C476%20crore%20to%20China%20to%20avoid%20payment%20of%20taxes%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20latest%20arrests%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-arrests-two-senior-employees-chinese-firm-vivo-source-2023-12-23%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVivo%20spokesperson%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20said%20that%20the%20the%20firm%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20deeply%20alarmed%20by%20the%20current%20action%20of%20the%20authorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20recent%20arrests%20demonstrate%20continued%20harassment%20and%20as%20such%20induce%20an%20environment%20of%20uncertainty%20amongst%20the%20wider%20industry%20landscape.%20We%20are%20resolute%20in%20using%20all%20legal%20avenues%20to%20address%20and%20challenge%20these%20accusations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20tightened%20the%20monitoring%20of%20activities%20of%20Chinese%20firms%20after%20the%20start%20of%20the%20border%20stand-off%20in%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703561726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26090416%2FScreenshot-2023-12-26-at-9.04.01%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fd