t%20the%20big%20question%20is%3A%20why%20are%20such%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20people%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20of%20London%20to%20support%20Palestine%3F%20Aren%E2%80%99t%20they%20working%20in%20favour%20of%20Hamas%3F%20When%20I%20asked%20this%20question%20to%20Corbyn%2C%20the%20old%20man%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20at%20all.%20This%20huge%20crowd%20is%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20against%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20cleansing%20in%20the%20name%20of%20fighting%20Hamas%2C%20against%20the%20slaughter%20of%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20including%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20all%2C%20it%20was%20Hamas%20who%20started%20the%20war%20on%20October%207.%20Corbyn%E2%80%99s%20answer%20was%20clear%20enough%3A%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20tell%20me%20that%20anti-colonial%20violence%20was%20started%20by%20the%20freedom%20fighters%20of%20India%20or%20Africa%3F%20Similarly%2C%20this%20war%20was%20not%20started%20by%20Hamas%20or%20the%20PLO.%20While%20the%20October%207%20violence%20should%20be%20condemned%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20carrying%20on%20with%20its%20occupation%20in%20Palestine%20since%201948%20and%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20an%20unfortunate%20response%20to%20that.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20eradicate%20the%20fundamental%20reason%20behind%20this%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20unjust%20occupation%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20such%20bold%20arguments%20will%20also%20face%20counter-arguments%2C%20the%20Palestine%20crisis%20will%20not%20move%20off%20the%20centrestage%20of%20British%20politics%20for%20some%20time%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703501902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25160650%2Fimage-1667.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-israel-palestine-war-is-shifting-the-political-dynamics-in-britain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20line%20with%20the%20US%2C%20the%20enti