gs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances)%20Act%20of%201985%2C%20a%20British%20national%20named%20Nigel%20had%20already%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20a%20year%20in%20jail.%20In%20early%20November%201994%20he%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Prisons%20requesting%20permission%20to%20perform%20a%20Christmas%20play%20within%20the%20prison%20complex.%20He%20also%20requested%20the%20Prison%20Administration%20for%20costumes%20and%20sound%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20ambitious%20request.%20Nothing%20of%20the%20sort%20had%20ever%20been%20attempted%20before.%20The%20IG%20decided%20to%20put%20Nigel%20in%20touch%20with%20us.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20foreign%20prisoner%20who%20wants%20to%20form%20a%20theater%20troupe%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20us.%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20help%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20We%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20Nigel%20the%20moment%20I%20met%20him.%20He%20was%20short%2C%20bearded%2C%20and%20animated%2C%20and%20reminded%20me%20a%20bit%20of%20the%20bad%20guy%20in%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EAir%20Force%20One%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20without%20the%20menace.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20had%20had%20a%20spiritual%20awakening%20of%20sorts%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20and%20felt%20compelled%20to%20share%20the%20joy%20of%20the%20Christmas%20story%20with%20all%208000%20inmates%20of%20Tihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20excited%20was%20he%20about%20his%20project%20that%20he%20had%20already%20assembled%20a%20theatre%20troupe%20from%20amongst%20the%20other%20foreign%20inmates%20and%20had%20begun%20rehearsals.%C2%A0%20He%20showed%20us%20the%20script%20he%20had%20written.%20It%20was%20original.%20His%20notes%20for%20the%20Third%20Act%20read%20thus%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAct%203%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScene%201%3A%20Joseph%20and%20Mary%20on%20way%20to%20Bethlehem.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScene%202%3A%20Joseph%20gets%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20police%20on%20false%20charges%20of%20possessing%20drugs%20and%20is%20thrown%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScene%203%3A%20There%2C%20he%20meets%20Noah%20who%20has%20been%20incarcerated%20for%20attempting%20to%20build%20a%20boat%20without%20a%20proper%20license.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%2C%20man.%20Needs%20a%20little%20masala%2C%20you%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckled%20as%20he%20introduced%20us%20to%20the%20actors%20in%20his%20ensemble.%20Inmates%20of%20various%20nationalities%2C%20some%20undertrials%20and%20others%2C%20convicts%2C%20were%20chosen%20to%20play%20the%20roles%20of%20the%20kings%2C%20the%20shepherds%20and%20the%20angels.%20A%20short%2C%20stocky%20Nigerian%20was%20selected%20to%20play%20Joseph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20asked%20Nigel%20the%20question%20that%20had%20been%20bothering%20me%20from%20the%20time%20we%20first%20heard%20about%20this%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20are%20you%20doing%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20Christmas%20play%20without%20a%20Mary%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nigel%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20see%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20Mary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20responded%20cheerily%20and%20introduced%20us%20to%20a%20tall%2C%20bald%2C%20unsmiling%20Dutchman.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20put%20a%20shawl%20and%20a%20lipstick%20on%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20worst%20fear%20had%20just%20been%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERehearsals%20were%20held%20for%20the%20play%20every%20morning%20and%20every%20evening%20for%202%20weeks.%20Also%20part%20of%20the%20play%20were%20Christmas%20carols%20to%20be%20performed%20by%20a%20choir%20of%2012%20Nigerian%20inmates.%20They%20looked%20good%20on%20stage%20and%20moved%20well%20together%20as%20they%20sang.%20The%20only%20problem%20was%20that%20most%20of%20them%20were%20tone%20deaf%20and%20Chuck%20and%20Thomas%2C%20the%20biggest%20and%20worst%20tempered%20of%20the%20lot%2C%20did%20not%20get%20along.%20But%20these%20were%20minor%20issues%20in%20the%20larger%20scheme%20of%20things.%20We%20had%20bigger%20things%20to%20worry%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20toughest%20part%20of%20the%20production%2C%20however%2C%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20choir!%20They%20just%20could%20not%20carry%20a%20tune.%20With%20only%20ten%20days%20to%20go%20for%20the%20first%20show%20and%20tensions%20running%20high%2C%20I%20called%20a%20friend%20who%20owned%20a%20studio%20and%20asked%20him%20for%20advice.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20create%20music%20tracks%20for%20you%20that%20these%20chaps%20can%20sing%20on.%20Make%20sure%20the%20music%20is%20louder%20than%20the%20vocals.%20It%20just%20might%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20did!%20The%20singers%20were%20thrilled%20to%20discover%20that%20they%20actually%20could%20sing%20karaoke%20style%20to%20backing%20music%20tracks.%20So%20inspired%20were%20they%20with%20their%20new%20ability%20to%20sound%20melodic%20that%20they%20practiced%20for%20two%20days%20straight%20without%20fighting%20and%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20the%20second%20day%20managed%20to%20sing%20%3Cem%3EJingle%20Bells%2C%20O%20Come%20All%20Ye%20faithful%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESilent%20Night%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20same%20key.%20The%20relief%20was%20huge.%20They%20fist%20bumped%20and%20high-fived%2C%20and%20that%20night%20I%20slept%20in%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecember%2018%2C%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20of%20the%20first%20Christmas%20show%20arrived.%20The%20Tihar%20Theatre%20Troupe%20was%20to%20debut%20in%20Jail%20No.%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigel%2C%20every%20inch%20the%20nervous%20director%2C%20gave%20last%20minute%20instructions%20to%20the%20actors%20who%20took%20up%20positions%20behind%20the%20stage.%20The%202000-strong%20population%20of%20the%20jail%20filed%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Echakkar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20common%20area%20used%20for%20cultural%20events%20and%20started%20sitting%20in%20rows%20under%20the%20watchful%20eyes%20of%20the%20white%20%3Cem%3Ekurta%20pajama%3C%2Fem%3E%20clad%20%3Cem%3Enumberdaars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20convicts%20charged%20with%20maintaining%20order%20amongst%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20inmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20327px)%2085vw%2C%20327px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25121447%2F81LnlRllM5L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22327%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25121447%2F81LnlRllM5L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20625w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25121447%2F81LnlRllM5L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-188x300.jpg%20188w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690663%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERohit%20Kumar%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ETales%20from%20the%20Jail%20%E2%80%93%20Christmas%20in%20Tihar%20and%20Other%20Stories%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ENotion%20Press%2C%202016%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20something%20unnerving%20about%20looking%20out%20over%20a%20sea%20of%20prison%20inmates%20sitting%20cross-legged%20in%20neat%20rows%20and%20waiting%20for%20a%20show%20to%20begin.%20Events%20at%20Tihar%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20style.%20Marigold%20garlands%20festooned%20the%20gigantic%20concrete%20stage%2C%20carpets%20covered%20it%20and%20a%20podium%20waited%20off%20to%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20was%20in%20English%20and%20since%20it%20needed%20a%20running%20translation%20in%20Hindi%2C%20I%20had%20volunteered%20to%20be%20the%20narrator-translator.%20There%20are%20things%20I%20have%20done%20years%20ago%20which%20still%20bring%20a%20smile%20to%20my%20face.%20Helping%20Nigel%20organize%20his%20play%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20Being%20his%20running%20translator%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20I%20had%20believed%20till%20that%20point%20that%20two%20thousand%20prisoners%20were%20going%20to%20watch%20a%20Christmas%20play%20performed%20by%20foreign%20inmates%20in%20respectful%20and%20appreciative%20silence%20I%20still%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%20But%20the%20moment%20%E2%80%98Mary%E2%80%99%20walked%20on%20to%20the%20stage%2C%20I%20realized%20respect%20and%20silence%20were%20not%20going%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%2C%20if%20you%20recall%2C%20was%20a%20tall%2C%20bald%20Dutchman.%20Dressed%20in%20a%20red%20saree%2C%20head%20covered%20by%20a%20brown%20shawl%2C%20and%20sporting%20a%20bright%20red%20bindi%20and%20even%20brighter%20lipstick%2C%20he%20looked%20grotesque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CJe%20kaun%20hai%20be%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%E2%80%9CWho%20the%20heck%20is%20that%3F%E2%80%9D)%20asked%20an%20inmate%20sitting%20in%20the%20front%20row%20in%20coarse%20Haryanvi%20in%20a%20stage%20whisper%20loud%20enough%20to%20be%20heard%20by%20at%20least%20thirty%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CManne%20toh%20vilayeti%20kinnar%20lage!%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%9CLooks%20like%20a%20foreign%20eunuch%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D)%20responded%20his%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20going%20as%20expected.%20And%20it%20was%20just%20the%20beginning.%20Jail%20No.%204%20was%20about%20to%20witness%20the%20most%20unintentionally%20funny%20comedy%20they%20had%20ever%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigel%20narrated%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20town%20of%20Nazareth%20lived%20a%20young%20woman%20called%20Mary.%20Mary%20had%20found%20favour%20with%20God.%20One%20night%20as%20she%20was%20sleeping%2C%20an%20angel%20entered%20the%20room.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20translated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20angel%20%E2%80%98Gabriel%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20jovial%20Italian%20walked%20onto%20stage%20with%20a%20decidedly%20un-angelic%20swagger.%20He%20stood%20over%20Mary%2C%20stretched%20out%20his%20arms%2C%20and%20announced%20in%20a%20singsong%20voice%2C%20%E2%80%9CHail%20Mary%2C%20full%20of%20grace%2C%20the%20Lord%20is%20with%20you!%20You%20are%20going%20to%20blessed%20with%20a%20son%20who%20will%20be%20known%20as%20the%20Saviour%20of%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%2C%20expressing%20appropriate%20awe%2C%20replied%20in%20thick%20Dutch%20accented%20English%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20how%20can%20this%20be%2C%20seeing%20I%20have%20never%20known%20a%20man%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20translate%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoseph%20(in%20deep%20voice)%3A%20%E2%80%9CHey%2C%20Mary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%20(in%20equally%20deep%20voice)%3A%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20Joseph%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoseph%20(in%20deep%20voice)%3A%20%E2%80%9CBethlehem%20is%20crowded.%20All%20the%20inns%20are%20full.%20What%20are%20we%20going%20to%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%3A%20(in%20equally%20deep%20voice)%20%E2%80%9CPlease%2C%20we%20have%20to%20find%20a%20room.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20give%20birth.%20The%20baby%20is%20about%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%20dissolved%20in%20peals%20of%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20Baby%20Jesus%20(a%20cloth%20doll)%20was%20about%20to%20come%20into%20the%20world%2C%20Joseph%20knelt%20beside%20Mary%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCome%20on%2C%20Mary%2C%20push!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%20I%20heard%20someone%20in%20the%20audience%20mimicking%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20cry.%20Others%20imitated%20and%20soon%20about%20a%20thousand%20people%20joined%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20it%20happened!%20The%20moment%20of%20Jesus%E2%80%99%20birth!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoseph%20stood%20up%2C%20holding%20not%20a%20cloth%20doll%20but%20a%20real%20live%20baby%20in%20his%20arms!%20The%20crowd%20went%20wild.%20I%20lost%20my%20power%20of%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20later%20discovered%2C%20some%20of%20our%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20the%20shepherds%20to%20be%20precise%20%E2%80%93%20had%20discovered%20a%20baby%20behind%20the%20stage.%20It%20was%20the%20child%20of%20a%20woman%20labourer%20who%20along%20with%20others%20had%20been%20brought%20into%20the%20jail%20to%20do%20construction%20work.%20The%20actors%20had%20%E2%80%98borrowed%E2%80%99%20the%20baby%20and%20managed%20to%20pass%20it%20on%20to%20Mary%20and%20Joseph%20on%20stage.%20It%20was%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20the%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20kings%20%E2%80%93%20dressed%20in%20Indian%20king%20costumes%20replete%20with%20Indian%20crowns%20and%20Indian%20beads%20%E2%80%93%20walked%20in%20and%20offered%20%E2%80%98gifts%20of%20gold%2C%20frankincense%20and%20myrrh%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20And%20as%20they%20knelt%20before%20Indian%20baby%20Jesus%2C%20the%20choir%20walked%20up%20on%20stage%2C%20surrounded%20the%20nativity%20scene%20and%20sang%20%E2%80%98Silent%20Night%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20never%20forget%20the%20silence%20that%20followed.%20The%20Nigerian%20choir%20sang%20pitch-perfect.%20They%20were%20magical!%20Was%20this%20the%20same%20choir%20that%20had%20come%20to%20blows%20just%20days%20before%3F%20The%20actors%20joined%20in%20as%20did%20those%20few%20in%20the%20audience%20who%20knew%20the%20carol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSilent%20Night%2C%20Holy%20Night%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20is%20calm%2C%20all%20is%20bright%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20they%20finished%20singing%2C%20a%20hush%20had%20fallen%20on%20the%20crowd.%20Some%20sort%20of%20heavenly%20peace%20had%20indeed%20descended%20on%20Jail%20No.%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20ended%20and%20Nigel%20gave%20one%20last%20speech.%20It%20was%20halting%20and%20went%20something%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFriends%2C%20I%20know%20Diwali%20was%20a%20difficult%20day%20for%20you.%20You%20wanted%20to%20spend%20it%20with%20your%20family%20but%20you%20spent%20it%20here%20in%20jail.%20This%20is%20my%20first%20Christmas%20away%20from%20home%20too.%20Mary%20and%20Joseph%20were%20far%20away%20from%20home%20too.%20In%20the%20company%20of%20strangers.%20And%20yet%2C%20they%20were%20not%20alone.%20Neither%20are%20we.%20Christmas%20reminds%20me%20that%20we%20are%20never%20alone%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20voice%20broke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.%20And%20when%20you%20think%20there%20is%20no%20hope%20left%2C%20something%20wonderful%20will%20happen.%20I%20know%20it%20will.%20And%20you%20will%20be%20given%20the%20strength%20to%20carry%20on.%20Tomorrow%20will%20be%20better%20than%20yesterday.%20Merry%20Christmas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20set%2C%20the%20crowd%20dispersed%20and%20started%20heading%20back%20to%20their%20barracks%20in%20high%20spirits.%20The%20actors%20laughed%2C%20hugged%20and%20congratulated%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20have%20since%20passed.%20I%20lost%20touch%20with%20Nigel%20and%20his%20team%20after%20he%20got%20acquitted.%20But%20every%20December%20I%20remember%20the%20Tihar%20Theatre%20Troupe%20and%20give%20thanks%20for%20the%20memory%20of%20Christmas%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3ETales%20from%20the%20Jail%20%E2%80%93%20Christmas%20in%20Tihar%20and%20Other%20Stories%3Cem%3E%2C%20an%20anthology%20of%20a%20prison%20counsellor%E2%80%99s%20memoirs%20by%20Rohit%20Kumar.%20The%20author%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20letsempathize%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703493025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25122227%2Fsaad-chaudhry-AqHIWSsF24I-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fchristmas-in-tihar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20December%20I%20remember%20the%20Tihar%20Theatre%20Troupe%20and%20give%20thanks%20for%20the%20memory%20of%20Christmas%201994.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fchristmas-in-tihar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lull%20in%20Highway%20Construction%20Expected%20in%20FY25%2C%20Flagship%20Highway%20Project%20Faces%206%20Year%20Delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26130435%2F30501593928_465a2ee4cf_c-e1682494521102.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20construction%20of%20national%20highways%20is%20expected%20to%20slow%20down%20in%20FY25%20on%20account%20of%20decline%20in%20projects%20awarded%20during%20FY24.%20Projects%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20just%202%2C817%20km%20were%20awarded%20till%20November%202023%2C%20compared%20to%205%2C382%20km%20during%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fa-slow-stretch-lies-ahead%2Farticle67669673.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20(MoRTH)%20said%20that%20approvals%20need%20to%20be%20expedited%20for%20the%20revised%20Bharatmala%20Phase-I%20project%20or%20any%20alternative%20programme%20to%20meet%20the%20targeted%20awards%20for%20FY24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shortfall%20may%20worsen%20with%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20effect%20during%20January-March%202024.%20March%20typically%20sees%20a%20significant%20percentage%20of%20road%20project%20awards%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fa-slow-stretch-lies-ahead%2Farticle67669673.ece%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICRA%2C%20a%20ratings%20agency%2C%20predicted%20a%20lower%20overall%20award%20in%20FY24%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20cutting%20its%20forecast%20to%207%2C000-7%2C500%20km%2C%20a%2040-43%25%20decline%20year-on-year.%20The%20delay%20in%20Cabinet%20approval%20for%20the%20revised%20cost%20of%20Bharatmala%20Phase-I%20has%20also%20slowed%20the%20project%20awarding%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20down%20the%20awarding%20process%2C%20Modani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fa-slow-stretch-lies-ahead%2Farticle67669673.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20award%2C%20say%2C%20in%20July%2C%20August%20or%20September%2C%20then%20financial%20closure%20and%20so%20on%20happen%20six%20months%20down%20the%20line%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20appointed%20date.%20So%2C%20it%20generally%20takes%208-9%20months%20for%20work%20to%20begin%20after%20the%20awarding.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20FY24%20will%20not%20be%20impacted%20because%20most%20projects%20are%20underway%20at%20a%20comfortable%20clip.%20However%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20slowdown%20in%20awarding%20during%20the%20current%20fiscal%2C%20then%20execution%20will%20be%20impacted%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20FY25%20and%2C%20subsequently%2C%20FY26%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ICRA%2C%20there%20is%20a%20preference%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98engineering%2C%20procurement%2C%20and%20construction%E2%80%99%20(EPC)%20route%20in%20road%20project%20awards%2C%20with%20a%20gradual%20shift%20towards%20%E2%80%98build%2C%20operate%20and%20transfer%E2%80%99%20(BOT)-toll%20projects%20which%20require%20less%20funding%20support%20from%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBharatmala%20Phase-I%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20extend%20the%20completion%20deadline%20for%20the%20flagship%20highway%20development%20project%2C%20Bharatmala%20Phase-I%2C%20from%202022%20to%202027-28.%20The%20six-year%20delay%20from%20the%20original%20schedule%20is%20primarily%20driven%20by%20a%20more%20than%20100%25%20increase%20in%20the%20estimated%20cost%20of%20the%20project%20which%20is%20now%20standing%20at%20nearly%20Rs%2011%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20ministry%20of%20road%20transport%20and%20highways%E2%80%99%20endeavour%20to%20award%20all%20projects%20on%20completion%20of%20land%20acquisition%20and%20obtaining%20all%20clearances%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024-25%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%20length%20of%2034%2C800%20km%2C%20approximately%2076%25%2C%20or%2026%2C418%20km%2C%20of%20highway%20stretches%20have%20been%20awarded%20so%20far.%20Despite%20this%20progress%2C%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%20the%20current%20financial%20year%20have%20seen%20only%20102%20km%20of%20projects%20under%20Bharatmala%20Phase-I%20being%20awarded%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20of%20awarding%20projects%20is%20expected%20to%20further%20slow%20down%20until%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20sanctions%20the%20revised%20cost%20of%20the%20project.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20has%20imposed%20restrictions%2C%20barring%20the%20highways%20ministry%20from%20creating%20any%20fresh%20liability%20under%20the%20project%20until%20CCEA%20approval%20is%20secured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20extended%20completion%20deadline%20set%20for%202027-28%2C%20only%2042%25%2C%20or%2015%2C045%20km%2C%20of%20the%20project%20had%20been%20completed%20as%20of%20November-end%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20committee%20initially%20approved%20the%20first%20phase%20in%202017%2C%20estimating%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%205.35%20trillion.%20However%2C%20the%20sanctioned%20cost%20of%20awarded%20projects%20has%20surpassed%20Rs%208.5%20trillion%2C%20prompting%20the%20Public%20Investment%20Board%20to%20appraise%20the%20revised%20cost%20of%20Bharatmala%20Phase-I%20at%20Rs%2010.95%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703491345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26130435%2F30501593928_465a2ee4cf_c-e1682494521102.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flull-in-highway-construction-expected-in-fy25-flagship-highway-projected-faces-6-year-delay%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shortfall%20may%20worsen%20with%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20effect%20during%20January-March%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flull-in-highway-construction-expected-in-fy25-flagship-highway-projected-faces-6-year-delay%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20BJP%20MP%2C%20Ex-WFI%20Head%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20Been%20Brought%20Down%20a%20Peg%20or%20Two%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F25124341%2FGA1OyoaXkAIKcph.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20meeting%20between%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20and%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20and%20party%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20suggests%20Singh%20may%20have%20become%20more%20powerful%20in%20the%20scheme%20of%20things%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20emerged%20saying%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20to%20do%20with%20wrestling%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20drew%20attention%20to%20how%20he%20still%20reigned%20supreme%20in%20the%20party.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20bigger%20tasks%20to%20accomplish%20%E2%80%93%20like%20the%202024%20general%20election.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1738848801140482326%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EPTI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CWFI%20elections%20were%20held%20on%20SC%20%5BSupreme%20Court%5D%20directions.%20Further%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20not%20my%20relative.%20To%20resume%20the%20sports%20activities%20and%20not%20waste%20a%20year%20of%20young%20wrestlers%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20conduct%20the%20games%20in%20Nandini%20Nagar.%20Now%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20wrestling%20and%20have%20to%20look%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20that%20are%20approaching.%20Whatever%20decision%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20new%20federation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20sport%20now.%20I%20have%20other%20responsibilities%20to%20focus%20now.%20I%20will%20be%20away%20from%20the%20politics%20of%20this%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fsanjay-singh-not-my-relative-says-brij-bhushan-on-suspension-of-wfi-backs-announcement-of-u-15-u-20-nationals-2823897%5C%22%3Ewrites%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20This%20would%20suggest%20he%20has%20just%20being%20taken%20off%20from%20wrestling%2C%20as%20the%20public%20attention%20as%20well%20as%20visible%20annoyance%20of%20the%20influential%20Jat%20community%20in%20Haryana%20was%20getting%20hard%20to%20avoid.%20But%20B.B.S.%20Singh%20remains%20central%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20plans%20in%20the%20future%20and%20it%20has%20not%20been%20ruled%20out%20by%20the%20party%20that%20he%20may%20be%20accommodated%20in%20a%20more%20powerful%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20previously%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20(directly%20under%20the%20control%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah)%20has%20never%20really%20moved%20on%20Singh%3B%20it%20took%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20to%20even%20get%20an%20FIR%20filed.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20told%20a%20court%20in%20September%20that%20the%20BJP%20MP%20had%20%E2%80%9Coutraged%20the%20modesty%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20women%20wrestlers.%20This%20was%20when%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20was%20hearing%20the%20case%20on%20framing%20of%20charges%20against%20him%20after%20the%C2%A0chargesheet%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20case%C2%A0filed%20by%20six%20women%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Flaw%2Fstory%2Fbrij-bhushan-singh-harassed-wrestlers-at-every-opportunity-delhi-police-to-court-2439705-2023-09-24%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%20Atul%20Srivastava%2C%20representing%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20WFI%20chief%20%E2%80%9Cknew%20what%20he%20was%20doing%E2%80%9D%20and%20his%20intention%20was%20to%20outrage%20the%20modesty%20of%20the%20wrestlers.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20are%20three%20types%20of%20evidence%20against%20Singh%20which%20are%20enough%20to%20frame%20charges.%20These%20include%20a%20written%20complaint%20and%20two%20recorded%20statements%20under%20Sections%20161%20(examination%20of%20witnesses%20by%20the%20police)%20and%20164%20(statements%20recorded%20by%20a%20magistrate)%20under%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC).%20Srivastava%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%20the%20court%20is%20within%20its%20jurisdiction%20to%20frame%20charges%20against%20Singh.%20He%20also%20countered%20the%20argument%20made%20by%20the%20WFI%20chief%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20that%20sanction%20under%20Section%20188%20of%20the%20CrPC%20is%20required%20for%20cases%20that%20took%20place%20outside%20India.%20But%20Singh%20continued%20to%20show%20growing%20impunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20meritorious%20students%20in%20his%20constituency%20of%20Gonda%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20how%20he%20had%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fdabang-since-childhood-failed-twice-in-class-8-says-brijbhushan-sharan-singh-while-felicitating-meritorious-students-2776476%5C%22%3Ethat%20he%20had%20been%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edabang%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(muscleman)%20since%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20he%20had%2C%20after%20failing%20twice%20in%20the%208th%20standard%2C%20one%20of%20his%20classmates%20write%20his%20answer%20sheets%20by%20threatening%20to%20%E2%80%98break%E2%80%99%20his%20bones%20if%20he%20(the%20classmate)%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20election%20of%20the%20new%20president%2C%20scenes%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Findia%2Fdabdaba-tha-dabdaba-rahega-says-brij-bhushan-singh-after-close-aide-wins-wfi-poll-1503251972.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edab%20daba%20thaa%2C%20dab%20daba%20rahega%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(we%20have%20had%20control%2C%20will%20retain%20control)%E2%80%9D%20emerged%2C%20with%20Singh%20being%20garlanded%20and%20feted%20%E2%80%93%20making%20clear%20there%20was%20no%20real%20change%20of%20guard.%20Medallist%20Sakshi%20Malik%20retired%20from%20wrestling%2C%20gold%20medallist%20Bajrang%20Punia%20said%20he%20was%20returning%20his%20Padmashree.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20that%2C%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20camp%20in%20Gonda%20(an%20area%20meant%20to%20be%20close%20to%20where%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20personal%20area%20of%20control%20and%20influence%20is)%20that%20the%20sports%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20Gonda%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20was%20only%20after%20his%20candidate%20(by%20his%20own%20admission)%20declared%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20new%20WFI%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20camp%20in%20Gonda%20(Singh%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency)%20that%20the%20sports%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWrestlers%20were%20beaten%20up%20and%20dragged%20off%20protesting%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20building%20of%20parliament%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5