%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhanush%20Biopic%20on%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%3A%20The%20Real%20Story%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Musical%20Sage%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIlaiyaraaja%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298846%2Fponniyin-selvan-must-watch-mani-ratnam-movies-yuva-alaipayuthey-nayakan-indian-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprolific%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20has%20seen.%20The%20composer%20has%20regaled%20millions%20with%20his%20tunes%20for%20over%20five%20decades.%20Fondly%20called%20Raaja%2C%20the%2080-year-old%20has%20fans%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Pannaipuram%20village%20in%20Theni%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20stormed%20into%20the%20music%20industry%20in%20the%2070s%2C%20and%20ruled%20the%20Tamil%20music%20industry%20for%20several%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20composed%20over%208%2C000%20songs%20in%201%2C000%20films%20and%20has%20enthralled%20audiences%20through%20his%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20conferred%20with%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20and%20five%20National%20Awards%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Isaignani%E2%80%99%20(the%20musical%20sage)%20and%20was%20conferred%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Maestro%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Royal%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%2C%20London%2C%20being%20the%20first%20Asian%20composer%20to%20record%20a%20symphony%20with%20them%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20credited%20with%20changing%20the%20way%20music%20is%20made%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247945%2Fsp-balasubrahmanyam-spb-padma-vibhushan-award-2021-singer-music-world-record-roja-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Tamil%20films.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20composers%20to