The%20outcome%20was%20a%20subscription-based%20model%20offering%20affordable%20rentals%20for%20toys%20and%20books.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334684%2Fmumbai-ca-dad-starts-a-toy-rental-business-rents-affordable-toys-for-kids%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20Ran%20My%20YouTube%20Channel%20From%20a%20Village%20With%20No%20Network%20To%20Break%20Meghalaya%20Food%20Stereotypes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENambie%20Jessica%20Marak%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20for%20her%20higher%20education.%20Hailing%20from%20Upper%20Rangsa%2C%20a%20village%20in%20the%20West%20Khasi%20Hills%20of%20Meghalaya%2C%20she%20missed%20home%20food.%20While%20she%20loved%20the%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebiryanis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20ached%20for%20her%20comfort%20food%20%E2%80%94%20a%20country%20chicken%20soup%20with%20fiddlehead%20ferns.%20Unfortunately%2C%20what%20she%20got%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326801%2Fvedhapriya-ganesan-snake-rescuer-wildlife-conservationist-pet-stylist-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETN%20capital%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20just%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20bothered%20her%20more%20was%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20Northeast%20culture%20and%20food.%20Wanting%20to%20educate%20her%20friends%20about%20the%20intricacies%20of%20her%20food%2C%20she%20looked%20for%20YouTube%20channels.%20Finding%20that%20most%20of%20the%20channels%20were%20in%20local%20languages%2C%20in%202015%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20start%20her%20own%20called%20%E2%80%98Eat%20Your%20Kappa%E2%80%99%20to%20document%20Northeastern%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20one%20of%20the%20few%20food%20bloggers%20from%20the%20region%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Nambie%20s